1
00:00:24,580 --> 00:00:27,420
Peter and Benjamin were planning a harvest feast.

2
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:34,200
"We need berries," Peter said.

3
00:00:36,860 --> 00:00:39,940
"Let's gather some nuts too," Benjamin said.

4
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:42,640
"A harvest feast must have nuts!"

5
00:00:50,060 --> 00:00:51,960
The bunnies gathered some berries.

6
00:01:01,300 --> 00:01:02,700
Then they looked for nuts.

7
00:01:09,900 --> 00:01:12,580
Peter and Benjamin saw lots of squirrels.

8
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:17,360
The squirrels were gathering nuts for winter.

9
00:01:20,240 --> 00:01:21,520
It was hard work!

10
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:30,840
Peter and Benjamin put their nuts in a pile.

11
00:01:31,460 --> 00:01:34,240
"We have a big pile now," Peter said.

12
00:01:34,540 --> 00:01:37,440
"Hey!" shouted a squirrel.

13
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:39,600
It was Timmy Tiptoes.

14
00:01:40,860 --> 00:01:42,720
Timmy ran toward the bunnies.

15
00:01:43,620 --> 00:01:45,480
He pointed at their big pile.

16
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:49,520
"Are you stealing my nuts?" he asked.

17
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:52,320
Timmy looked at Benjamin and Peter.

18
00:01:54,020 --> 00:01:55,560
"No," Peter said.

19
00:01:56,060 --> 00:01:57,620
"We collected these nuts."

20
00:02:00,440 --> 00:02:02,860
"Hmph!" Timmy looked mad.

21
00:02:04,140 --> 00:02:06,340
"I put my nuts right there."

22
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:10,820
"Well, these are our nuts," Benjamin said.

23
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:13,600
Timmy frowned.

24
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:16,620
"Then where are my nuts?"

25
00:02:17,740 --> 00:02:20,360
Benjamin shrugged. "I don't know."

26
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:29,600
"But we will find out!" Peter said.

27
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:08,240
Peter and Benjamin looked for the missing nuts.

28
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:19,320
Timmy gathered new ones.

29
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:31,640
"The squirrels are very busy," Peter said.

30
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:34,260
"They are gathering lots of nuts."

31
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:39,420
"Winter is coming," Benjamin said. "They need—"

32
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:42,640
"Hey!" A squirrel suddenly shouted.

33
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:46,920
"Look at my pile!" a second squirrel cried.

34
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:51,180
"Who stole my nuts?" a third squirrel yelled.

35
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:55,680
More squirrels came running.

36
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:59,460
One squirrel shouted at Timmy Tiptoes.

37
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:03,360
"Did you steal our nuts?" she cried.

38
00:04:04,100 --> 00:04:05,780
"No!" Timmy said.

39
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:08,840
"Someone took some of my nuts too."

40
00:04:09,780 --> 00:04:11,460
"There is a nut thief!"

41
00:04:13,260 --> 00:04:15,540
The squirrels shouted back and forth.

42
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:23,580
Just then Peter spotted a fat squirrel.

43
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:28,800
"Look, Benjamin!" Peter whispered.

44
00:04:29,460 --> 00:04:30,640
"It's Silvertail."

45
00:04:32,100 --> 00:04:34,880
Silvertail slipped over to the nut piles.

46
00:04:36,340 --> 00:04:38,280
The squirrels were still fighting.

47
00:04:39,180 --> 00:04:41,100
They did not see Silvertail.

48
00:04:42,820 --> 00:04:44,600
He took nuts from a pile!

49
00:05:04,660 --> 00:05:07,320
Silvertail hid the nuts under a log.

50
00:05:09,980 --> 00:05:11,540
Then he laughed.

51
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:18,780
"I have lots of nuts for winter. I don't have to work at all!"

52
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:48,700
Peter looked at Benjamin.

53
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:51,120
"Silvertail is the nut thief!"

54
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:58,420
The bunnies ran to the squirrels.

55
00:06:00,340 --> 00:06:02,920
"We found the nut thief!" Peter said.

56
00:06:04,620 --> 00:06:06,800
"Go away!" a squirrel said.

57
00:06:07,260 --> 00:06:10,460
"This is not bunny business," another yelled.

58
00:06:11,100 --> 00:06:12,800
"It is squirrel business!"

59
00:06:14,140 --> 00:06:15,840
Timmy looked at the bunnies.

60
00:06:16,580 --> 00:06:19,200
"Who is the nut thief?" he asked.

61
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:22,520
"Come with us," Benjamin said.

62
00:06:23,180 --> 00:06:24,180
"We will show you."

63
00:06:26,980 --> 00:06:28,660
Timmy followed the bunnies.

64
00:06:38,020 --> 00:06:40,500
They showed him Silvertail's hiding spot.

65
00:06:43,540 --> 00:06:45,340
Timmy's eyes got big.

66
00:06:45,980 --> 00:06:48,040
"Wow!" he said.

67
00:06:48,700 --> 00:06:51,540
"Silvertail is stealing our nuts!"

68
00:06:51,590 --> 00:06:53,860
"We must stop him."

69
00:06:56,180 --> 00:06:58,120
Benjamin saw a hollow tree.

70
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,650
It had a hole in its trunk.

71
00:07:00,700 --> 00:07:07,760
"Hmm," Benjamin said. "I have an idea."

72
00:07:09,740 --> 00:07:11,360
The bunnies got some nuts.

73
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,980
They hopped to the hollow tree.

74
00:07:20,820 --> 00:07:23,080
Then they pushed the nuts into the hole.

75
00:07:25,740 --> 00:07:29,640
"Now let's find Silvertail!" Benjamin said.

76
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:46,200
Silvertail was taking a nap.

77
00:07:46,740 --> 00:07:54,020
"Hi, Silvertail!" Peter woke him up.

78
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:58,110
"We found lots of nuts.

79
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:59,960
Would you like some?"

80
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:06,220
"Yes!" Silvertail licked his lips.

81
00:08:07,220 --> 00:08:09,720
"Where are they?"

82
00:08:24,820 --> 00:08:26,960
The bunnies brought Silvertail to the tree.

83
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:32,080
Silvertail looked in the hole.

84
00:08:36,060 --> 00:08:38,200
"I don't see any nuts."

85
00:08:38,250 --> 00:08:41,000
Silvertail bent deeper.

86
00:08:41,050 --> 00:08:43,500
"Where are—Yikes!"

87
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:46,100
Silvertail fell into the hole.

88
00:08:46,540 --> 00:08:48,900
"Ahh!" he cried.

89
00:08:48,950 --> 00:08:52,440
"I'm stuck!"

90
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,520
The bunnies laughed.

91
00:08:58,660 --> 00:09:01,500
"The nut thief is trapped!" Peter said.

92
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:05,800
"Good-bye, Silvertail!" Benjamin said.

93
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:15,140
The bunnies told the squirrels about Silvertail.

94
00:09:16,940 --> 00:09:18,580
The squirrels stopped fighting.

95
00:09:19,140 --> 00:09:21,760
"I have a great idea," Timmy said.

96
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:24,200
"Let's share our nuts!"

97
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:33,680
The squirrels shared all the nuts.

98
00:09:35,020 --> 00:09:36,800
Timmy gave some to the bunnies.

99
00:09:39,140 --> 00:09:42,000
"Thank you for helping us," Timmy said.

100
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:46,020
"We can save these nuts for our feast!" Peter said.

101
00:09:51,900 --> 00:09:54,400
At last it was time for the harvest feast.

102
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:57,520
All the squirrels came.

103
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:04,320
Timmy rubbed his belly.

104
00:10:05,580 --> 00:10:08,140
"These nut pies are delicious!"

105
00:10:09,820 --> 00:10:11,560
Then someone else appeared.

106
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:15,080
Peter gasped. "Silvertail!"

107
00:10:15,560 --> 00:10:16,860
Benjamin laughed.

108
00:10:19,900 --> 00:10:21,940
"He's not fat anymore!"

109
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,520
Silvertail frowned at the bunnies.

110
00:10:26,100 --> 00:10:28,120
"You trapped me in the tree!"

111
00:10:28,170 --> 00:10:30,580
"And where are all my nuts?"

112
00:10:32,220 --> 00:10:34,200
Peter pointed to the nut pies.

113
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:36,000
"Right there."

114
00:10:36,380 --> 00:10:40,020
Everyone—but Silvertail—laughed.

